anon_pretext1: Ho netefatsa hore sesebelisoa sa hau se kentsoe 'me se fumane Inthanete, tobetsa Kena. Khokahano e tla lula e le teng lihora tse 12 ntle le ho sebedisa sesebelisoa sena.
status_pretext1: Sesebelisoa sa hau se kentsoe 'me se fumane Inthanete. Khokahano e tla lula e le teng ka nako e behiloeng ke tsamaiso ea marang-rang ho latela ts'ebetso ea sesebelisoa sena.
status_pretext2: Haeba u batla ho fela ka khokahano ena ka boikhethelo, tobetsa TLOHELA HO KENA.
noscript: Tsebiso: Ho kena ka nepo ho hloka hore JavaScript e sebelisoe sebatli.
cp_portal_head_title: Sisteme sa ho kena ea basebelisi
cp_portal_info: Ho fihlella Inthanete ho marang-rang <Lebitso la ISP> ho hloka ho kenya lebitso la mosebedisi le phasewete. Hopola hore phasewete le lebitso la mosebedisi li lokela ho sireletsoa ke mosebedisi.
cp_portal_cookies_note: Sisteme sa ho kena sa basebelisi se sebelisa li-cookies ho boloka tlhahisoleseling khomphuteng ea hau. Re sebelisa li-cookies ho fana ka litšebeletso tse phahameng, ho kenyeletsa le ho ikamahanya le litlhoko tsa mosebedisi. Ho sebelisa portal ea ho kena ntle le ho fetola li-setting tsa li-cookies ho bolela hore li tla bolokoa sesebelisoa sa hau.
cp_session_time_left: Nako e setseng ea ho fela ha sehlopha:
cp_session_time_left_less_than_minute: metsotso e ka tlase ho e le 'ngoe
cp_session_timeout_content:
Nako e fanoeng ea ho fihlella Inthanete e felile, kahoo khokahano e felile.
Seo u ka se etsang?
  • Ho tsoela pele ho sebelisa Inthanete, hlahloba hore na ho ka atolosoa kapa u reke nako e eketsehileng.
  • Haeba u na le lipotso, ikopanye le ts'ebeletso ea theknoloji.
cp_error_login_err: Lebitso la mosebedisi kapa phasewete ha le nepahale
cp_error_title: Phoso ea Sisteme ea ho Kena
cp_error_server_connection: Ha ho khonehe ho hokela seva ea netefatso
cp_error_info_title: Ho ka etsahala hore u sa khone ho kena ka lebaka la
cp_error_info:
• Lebitso la mosebedisi kapa phasewete e sebelisitsoeng ha le nepahale
  • Caps Lock e tobetsa khomphuteng
  • Khomphutha e 'ngoe e kene ka ak'haonte ea hau
  • Ak'haonte ea hau e thibetsoe ke tsamaiso ka lebaka la ts'ebetso e mpe ea sesebelisoa sa hau
  • Bokhoni ba ak'haonte bo felile kapa bo hlakotsoe ka lebaka la ho se lefe tefo ea tefo
cp_error_solution_title: Leka ho rarolla bothata ka ho latela litlhahiso tse ka tlase:
cp_error_solution:
• Hlahloba hore na u ngola lebitso la mosebedisi le phasewete ka nepo (hopola boholo ba litlhaku)
  • Hlahloba hore na ak'haonte ea hau e le tefello
  • Haeba bothata bo sa lumellane le litharollo tse kaholimo, ikopanye le tsamaiso ea marang-rang

cp_login_attempt_content: Sisteme e lumella ho pheta phoso ea ho kena makhetlo a %s. Ha palo e fete, monyetla oa ho kena o tla thibeloa ka nako ea %s %s.
a11y-keys_data-content:
Kopano ea likonopo
⇧ Shift (le letsoho le letšehali)
+ ⌥ Alt (le letsoho le letšehali)
+ tlhaku

⇧ Shift + ⌥ Alt + U
tšoara lebokose la Lebitso la mosebedisi

⇧ Shift + ⌥ Alt + P
tšoara lebokose la Phasewete

⇧ Shift + ⌥ Alt + A
hlahloba/ha hlahlobe lebokose la "Ke amohela molao-motheo"

⇧ Shift + ⌥ Alt + R
bula fensetere ea molao-motheo

⇧ Shift + ⌥ Alt + I
kena mosebedisi

⇧ Shift + ⌥ Alt + O
tlohela ho kena mosebedisi

⇧ Shift + ⌥ Alt + L
qalo ea phetoho ea puo
a11y-lang-keys_data-content:
Tobetsa 'me u tšoare ⇧ Shift (letsoho le letšehali) 'me u tobetse litlhaku tse peli tsa khoutu ea puo (ISO 639-1) ka nako e le 'ngoe kapa ka tatellano.

Mehlala:
⇧ Shift + P + L → fetola ho Sepolishe (pl)

⇧ Shift + E + N → fetola ho Se-english (en)

⇧ Shift + D + E → fetola ho Sejeremane (de)

⇧ Shift + F + R → fetola ho Sefora (fr)

⇧ Shift + E + S → fetola ho Sepanish (es)

⇧ Shift + I + T → fetola ho Seitaliane (it)
...
polyglotLanguageSwitcher_data-content: Mona u ka fetola mofuta oa puo ea portal. Ka ho tobetsa konopo ea keyboard %s u tla bula lebokose la %s kapa Shift le litlhaku tse peli tsa khoutu ea puo ka nako e le 'ngoe kapa ka tatellano, mohlala: Shift + P + L e fetola ho phetolelo e khethiloeng.
